    		<div class="sikhay-is-a">SIKHAY is a collaborative networking platform built exclusively for Honorians, the students of Pampanga State University. Our mission is to connect students with their peers to complete academic or campus‑related tasks, share study materials, and collectively own specialized equipment needed for certain subjects. SIKHAY fosters financial efficiency, accountability, and community spirit by reducing unnecessary expenses, encouraging cooperation, and strengthening togetherness among students. Whether it is posting queries, running errands, tutoring, or sharing reviewers and resources, SIKHAY provides a safe and verified environment where students can support one another. By requiring PSU email verification, we ensure that the platform remains authentic and focused on the needs of our academic community. SIKHAY is more than a website — it is a student‑driven initiative that promotes responsibility, collaboration, and lasting connections across the university. <br></div>
